  "worklog": "# brainTrade Work Log\n*Check this anytime to see what I'm doing and how I'm thinking.*\n\n## 2026-05-03 20:48 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 1] BTC breaks 15M again, ecb6 cuts hard\n\n**Task:** Re-check P1 copy intelligence after BTC held above `$17M` but `ecb6` slipped below `$5M`, focusing on whether BTC sustains bullish notional or falls back into distribution watch.\n\n**Finding:**\n- Both bots are alive (`pm-bot`, `hl-bot`).\n- Rotation pointed to **P1**.\n- Fresh tracker output: **BTC 7L/1S**, **ETH 2L/6S**, **SOL 2L/5S**.\n- Current top-book notional: BTC **+$14.72M net long**, ETH **-$34.32M net short**, SOL **-$10.94M net short**, HYPE **-$10.67M net short**, JTO **+$355 net long only**.\n- BTC broke the distribution trigger again: prior net **+$18.07M**, current net **+$14.72M**, trigger **<$15M** active again.\n- BTC count still looks superficially bullish at **7L/1S**, but notional quality deteriorated sharply.\n- `anon-0xecb6` BTC LONG cut from **$4.69M** to **$3.36M**.\n- `beatmaker1@proton.me` BTC LONG cut from **$2.14M** to **$447K**.\n- `anon-0xfc66` BTC LONG steady at **$5.63M**.\n- `anon-0x8fcc` BTC LONG steady at **$4.30M**, still below preferred **$5M** anchor.\n- `anon-0xf5d8` BTC SHORT remains present at **$213K**.\n- ETH remains high-conviction bearish: **2L/6S**, net **-$34.32M**, with `anon-0x3bca` ETH SHORT still **$1.41M**.\n- SOL remains high-conviction bearish by notional: **2L/5S**, net **-$10.94M**.\n- HYPE remains bearish by count and notional: **2L/7S**, net **-$10.67M**.\n- JTO top-trader confirmation remains absent.\n- I wrote the artifact to `/home/ubuntu/clawd/research/p1-btc-breaks-15m-again-ecb6-cuts-hard-2026-05-03-2048.md`.\n\n**My thinking:** BTC lost the bullish notional regime. The headline count is still 7L/1S, but the two important rebuilders (`ecb6`, `beatmaker1`) both cut hard, pulling net back below the `$15M` distribution trigger. This invalidates the near-clean bullish read and reactivates defensive/distribution watch.\n\n**Decision:** Downgrade BTC from **bullish notional / near-clean caveated** to **distribution watch / defensive overlay**. Full defensive hard trigger still requires BTC net **<$10M** or `anon-0x8fcc` flipping short above **$2M**. Reclaim condition: BTC net must recover **>$15M** for watch relief and **>$17M** plus stronger anchors for bullish context. Keep ETH bearish confidence high. Keep SOL bearish confidence high. Keep HYPE bearish confidence high. Keep PM weekend block active; no Sunday exception. Keep HL live notional-blocked; no forced trades from `$37.39`. Do not treat JTO P3 momentum as copy-intel confirmed.\n\n**Next:** Watch whether BTC net quickly reclaims **>$15M** or confirms distribution by staying below it while `ecb6`/`beatmaker1` continue trimming. If BTC net breaks **<$10M**, escalate to hard defensive downgrade.\n\n## 2026-05-03 20:38 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 4] Compression normalizes, BTC RANGE/UP\n\n**Task:** Refresh P4 alpha after compression eased to neutral range at 20:12 and test whether BTC finally normalizes",
